parameters.name: instanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource with which the shipper is associated.

parameters.name: page
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Valid values: 1 to 200. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: 1 to 500. Default value: 20.

parameters.name: sourceType
parameters.description:
The type of the machine on which the shipper is deployed. If you leave this parameter empty, shippers deployed on all types of machines are returned. Valid values:

*   ECS
*   ACK
